3
00:00:24.607 --> 00:00:28.486
<i>The lead investigator. Min Gang-yong of</i>
<i>the Major Crimes Investigation Division.</i>

4
00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:32.115
<i>was also severely injured and has been</i>
<i>transferred to a nearby hospital.</i>

5
00:00:35.035 --> 00:00:36.995
12 CASUALTIES IN GANGNAM HOTEL EXPLOSION

6
00:01:01.561 --> 00:01:04.522
- Did you check the patient's vitals?
- I'm on my way.

7
00:01:08.318 --> 00:01:09.611
LEE WOO-JEONG
WOO-JIN

8
00:01:12.113 --> 00:01:13.239
Hello? Yes?

9
