You're on a group call.
It's Woo-jeong. Are you there?

10
00:01:16.618 --> 00:01:18.203
- Yes.
- <i>I'm here. Woo-jeong.</i>

11
00:01:18.286 --> 00:01:19.829
Where are you both right now?

12
00:01:19.913 --> 00:01:22.916
